  "description": "<ul><li><strong>Well Established Japanese F&B Company</strong></li><li><strong>Salary UP$2700 + Incentive</strong></li><li><strong>Variable Bonus + Meal Provided</strong></li><li><strong>Working hours: 5.5 Days</strong></li><li><strong>Working Location: Queenstown</strong></li><li><strong>On-Job Training Provided</strong></li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Greet customers.</li><li>Attend to customer needs & requests in a pleasant manner.</li><li>Serving, taking orders & clearing tables.</li><li>Provide good customer service.</li><li>Promote menu items.</li><li>Restaurant Daily Opening / Closing duties.</li><li>Cashiering duties.</li><li>Be able to handle your assigned table of customers confidently.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>GCE O Level and above</li><li>0 – 2 years related experience in F&B</li></ul><p>Candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button with the following information in the resume:</p><ul><li>Work experiences and job responsibilities</li><li>Current and Expected salary</li><li>Reason for leaving</li><li>Date of availability</li><li>Education background</li></ul><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be contacted.</p><p>YEOW CHANG FU (R23118759)<br />EA Recruitment Pte Ltd<br />EA License No: 21C0492</p>",
